---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects — Chan Nirak Choun" currentPage="projects">

  <h1>Projects</h1>

  <h2>Flashly</h2>
  <div class="entry">
    <div class="entry-subtitle">Aug 2025 – Oct 2025</div>
    <ul>
      <li>Designed an event-driven microservice architecture using Spring Cloud (Gateway, Eureka, Config) and Kafka.</li>
      <li>Engineered a full security stack with a dedicated Auth Service (issuing JWTs) and a Resource Server (API Gateway).</li>
      <li>Developed a responsive Angular frontend and integrated backend services with PostgreSQL, Redis, and Docker.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Spring Boot</span>
      <span class="tag">Angular</span>
      <span class="tag">Kafka</span>
      <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
      <span class="tag">Redis</span>
      <span class="tag">Docker</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Vehicle Camera Health Monitor</h2>
  <div class="entry">
    <div class="entry-subtitle">May 2024 – Aug 2024</div>
    <ul>
      <li>Engineered a real-time health and battery monitoring system for in-vehicle IoT cameras using C++.</li>
      <li>Implemented a low-latency data pipeline (&lt;10ms) for transmitting live camera status and diagnostics.</li>
      <li>Developed a JavaScript-based web dashboard to visualize real-time diagnostics from multiple camera units.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">C++</span>
      <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
      <span class="tag">IoT</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Real-Time Emotion Recognition</h2>
  <div class="entry">
    <div class="entry-subtitle">May 2024 – Aug 2024</div>
    <ul>
      <li>Built and trained a computer vision model to detect facial emotions (happy, sad, energetic) in real-time.</li>
      <li>Engineered a high-performance C++ and Python pipeline to run the model on low-power IoT devices.</li>
      <li>Optimized the algorithm for low-latency feedback and efficient processing on embedded hardware.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">C++</span>
      <span class="tag">Python</span>
      <span class="tag">OpenCV</span>
      <span class="tag">IoT</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tools Section -->
  <h2>Tools & Technologies</h2>
  <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Languages</h3>
    <div class="tags" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
      <span class="tag">C/C++</span>
      <span class="tag">Python</span>
      <span class="tag">CUDA</span>
      <span class="tag">SQL</span>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">ML Systems & Hardware</h3>
    <div class="tags" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
      <span class="tag">LLVM</span>
      <span class="tag">MLIR</span>
      <span class="tag">TVM</span>
      <span class="tag">XLA</span>
      <span class="tag">Triton</span>
      <span class="tag">ONNX / ONNX Runtime</span>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">ML Libraries</h3>
    <div class="tags" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
      <span class="tag">PyTorch</span>
      <span class="tag">TensorFlow</span>
      <span class="tag">JAX</span>
      <span class="tag">Scikit-learn</span>
      <span class="tag">NumPy</span>
      <span class="tag">Pandas</span>
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Developer Tools</h3>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Git</span>
      <span class="tag">Docker</span>
      <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
